title: A10 Loadbalancer: Power Supplies
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/a10
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the power supplies of A10 Networks ADC loadbalancers
 via SNMP (A10-AX-MIB, axPowerSupply table).

 The service reports {OK} when a power supply is on, {CRIT} when it is
 reported as absent and {WARN} when it is off or in an unknown state.

discovery:
 One service is created for each power supply that is reported as present
 (status on).

item:
 The name of the power supply as reported by the device.
